Package: circbayes
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Analysis of Circular Data
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Author: Kees Mulder
Maintainer: The package maintainer <keestimmulder@gmail.com>
Description: The package `circbayes` collects methods for Bayesian analyses of circular data.  Included methods are regression, hypothesis testing, mixture models and nonparametric Dirichlet Process Models. 
